{"tid":83512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流浪漢手寫CV求職 善心人傳開有工做了","createTime":"2017-01-16T19:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T01:52:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4c25f1a2f226cee04547735f94332414777d2e","tid":83512,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:19:26.000Z","msg":"為求找到好工，人人都會「執靚」履歷表，但有人卻憑這張看似馬虎的手寫CV覓得工作，更引來不同範疇的老闆意欲聘用。他並非商場天之驕子，他只是英國利物浦一位「三失」流浪漢。<br />\n<br />\n20歲流浪漢洛基特（Jordan Lockett）一直想自食其力，但苦無機會，早前他得好心人出手相助，親筆寫下一紙簡單履歷，由對方代為放上網求職，結果反應出乎意料之外。<br />\n<br />\n「需要工作、需要幫忙、嚴重迷失」洛基特在履歷沒有咬文嚼字，用最淺白的表達方式指自己曾做過電單車維修技工，勤力好學，只是等一個機會。<br />\n<br />\n該手寫CV在社交網瘋傳後，許多僱主被他的真誠打動，有餐廳東主表示可教他烹飪及融入社會技巧，甚至可以預支薪水助渡難關；有速遞公司或管理企業也想給予機會。事件更引來市長安德森（Joe Anderson）關注，希望聯絡到洛基特，提供相關協助。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150715/53973629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20150715%2F53973629&d=cGojPhn2gm67rgLo28HS7nvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=15b98313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20150715%2F53973629&h=486a6b79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20150715/53973629</a>"},{"pid":"c67d8fce84df8e76f7d97b30ca89c8c42ed6fba5","tid":83512,"uid":11211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:29:10.000Z","msg":"係香港死撚左<br />\nd 人會幫你煲大黎恥笑<br />\n直接打入地獄"},{"pid":"99076ed22599ead52e3396d695a295d52ff7b7c8","tid":83512,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:41:50.000Z","msg":"根本係廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇cv你都識去見m記嗰啲嘛？<br />\n有錢去圖書館借電腦打cv，拎去print又好、send上網又好，20歲連依啲嘢都唔識仲想搵份工<br />\n請你返嚟你洗唔洗又求人幫你做埋你嗰份呀？"},{"pid":"fb8b5a2287308cc7604dd3f18213d52a6cb569c8","tid":83512,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:45:54.000Z","msg":"左膠新聞特別on9<br />\n之前又有咩流浪漢去試鞋，之後店員夾錢送畀佢<br />\non99"},{"pid":"7337f1c3712ba6a840bf51a05a8139760c705927","tid":83512,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"先廿歲人搵份工都要人幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad54ae0e26e285e870cbdc9feaded44ac1f510f","tid":83512,"uid":2832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T19:59:51.000Z","msg":"最近去過英國<br />\n周街勁多homeless<br />\n聽個係英國住嘅朋友講英國福利好好<br />\nhomeless 每個月有成皮資助<br />\n好多人都唔做野去homeless 等政府養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3367ea7add7ec62a5fabf764e1eeec66c9a63d8d","tid":83512,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近去過英國<br />\n周街勁多homeless<br />\n聽個係英國住嘅朋友講英國福利好好<br />\nhomeless 每個月有成皮資助<br />\n好多人都唔做野去homeless 等政府養<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n問題係homeless 好難搵嘢做。佢無地址電話人哋搵唔到佢，無銀行户口又因爲無地址開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}